    "spell": {
        "name": "Armor of Thorn and Claw",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "Razor-sharp thorns and claws erupt from your skin or scales. Whenever a creature touches you or hits you with a melee unarmed attack, it takes 1 piercing damage. Additionally, if you become grabbed, restrained, or otherwise held immobilized in a creature\u2019s grasp, such as by being engulfed or swallowed, the creature takes 1d4 persistent bleed damage.",
